id: pm-8ngt
title: "As a platform developer, I can build a non-PM domain system (e.g. a git-like VCS or a company's business workflows) using only pm SDK primitives"
description: "Horizon-5 exploration story: prove the pm SDK is a universal event-sourced application platform, not a PM-only toolkit. Inventories the primitive gaps a foreign domain exposes and feeds them back as concrete SDK items. Dedupe-checked 2026-07-06: pm search for VCS/business-logic/beyond-PM coverage found only the vision ADR pm-oxq5 and PM-domain stories pm-w89s/pm-cbwg; no item tracks the beyond-PM ambition."
